<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <!--Meta Data-->
    <%- include('partial/title.ejs'); %> 

    <% if (data.NODE_ENV == 'production') { %>
      <!-- Production Stylesheets -->
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/production/css/about.min.css">

    <% }else { %>
      <!-- Development Stylesheets -->
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/bootstrap.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/fontawesome.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/responsive.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/select2.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/spacing.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/style.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/owl.carousel.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/bootstrap-datepicker.min.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/magnific-popup.css">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/header.css">
      
    <% } %>
  </head>

  <body onLoad="typeWriter()">
    <!--Header-->
    <%- include('partial/header.ejs', {data: data }); %>

    <!--FAQ Start-->
    <div class="faq-area pt_60 pb_90">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12">
            <div class="faq-group headstyle mt-30">
              <div id="accordion">
                <div class="faq-item card">
                  <div class="faq-header" id="heading1">
                    <button class="faq-button " data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true"
                      aria-controls="collapse1"><i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i>How do I book an appointment using your platform??</button>
                  </div>

                  <div id="collapse1" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="heading1" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="faq-body">
                      <p>Booking an appointment is simple. Just log in to your account, select the healthcare provider you wish to see, choose a convenient date and time from their availability, and confirm your booking. You'll be able to see all details regarding bookings on your patient portal</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item card">
                  <div class="faq-header" id="heading2">
                    <button class="faq-button collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2"
                      aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2"><i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i>What happens if I need to cancel or reschedule my appointment??</button>
                  </div>

                  <div id="collapse2" class="collapse " aria-labelledby="heading2" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="faq-body">
                      <p>If you need to cancel or reschedule your appointment, simply log in to your account, go to your appointments, and select the option to cancel or reschedule. Please note that there may be specific cancellation policies depending on the healthcare provider.<br></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item card">
                  <div class="faq-header" id="heading3">
                    <button class="faq-button collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse3"
                      aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse3"><i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i>Is my personal information secure on your platform?</button>
                  </div>

                  <div id="collapse3" class="collapse " aria-labelledby="heading3" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="faq-body">
                      <p>Yes, we take the security and privacy of your personal information very seriously. Our platform uses advanced encryption techniques to protect your data, and we adhere to strict privacy policies to ensure that your information remains confidential.<br></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item card">
                  <div class="faq-header" id="heading4">
                    <button class="faq-button collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse4"
                      aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse4"><i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i>Can I view my past appointments and medical history on the platform?</button>
                  </div>

                  <div id="collapse4" class="collapse " aria-labelledby="heading4" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="faq-body">
                      <p>Yes, you can view your past appointments and medical history through your account dashboard. This feature allows you to keep track of your healthcare interactions and access important information when needed.<br></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item card">
                  <div class="faq-header" id="heading5">
                    <button class="faq-button collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse5"
                      aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse5"><i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i>Are there any restrictions on who can use the platform?</button>
                  </div>

                  <div id="collapse5" class="collapse " aria-labelledby="heading5" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="faq-body">
                      <p>Our platform is designed to be accessible to everyone. However, certain services may have age restrictions or specific requirements. For example, minors may need parental consent for certain appointments or services.<br></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item card">
                  <div class="faq-header" id="heading6">
                    <button class="faq-button collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse6"
                      aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse6"><i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i>How far in advance can I book an appointment?</button>
                  </div>

                  <div id="collapse6" class="collapse " aria-labelledby="heading6" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="faq-body">
                      <p>The booking window for appointments may vary depending on the healthcare provider's availability. Typically, you can book appointments up to several weeks in advance. However, for urgent appointments, you may be able to book for the same day or within a few days.<br></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <!--FAQ End-->

    <!--Footer-->
    <%- include('partial/footer.ejs'); %>
    
    <script>
      var i = 0;
      var txt = 'WELCOME TO DocConnect';
      var speed = 60;

      function typeWriter() {
        if (i < txt.length) {
          document.getElementById("typeit").innerHTML += txt.charAt(i);
          i++;
          setTimeout(typeWriter, speed);
        }
      }
    </script>

      <!-- JavaScript -->
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/jquery-3.4.1.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/all.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/lib/js/select2.full.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="assets/js/about.js"></script>
    
  </body>
</html>